---
export const label = 'Challenger; confrontational, direct';
---

<section class="py-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
      You don't need a dev shop. You need a builder.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
      You've got the vision, the market, and the drive. You're not looking for a
      team of strangers to manage &mdash; you're looking for one person who gets
      it and owns it. Architecture to deployment. No hand-offs, no layers, no
      surprises.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
